&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;/div></description></item><item><title>解决任务栏新建的 Edge 窗口使用不同配置文件的问题</title><link>https://thejiahao.github.io/posts/edge-window-different-profile-issue/</link><pubDate>Mon, 25 Dec 2023 09:30:20 +0200</pubDate><guid>https://thejiahao.github.io/posts/edge-window-different-profile-issue/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://thejiahao.github.io/posts/edge-window-different-profile-issue/edge_logo.svg" alt="Featured image of post 解决任务栏新建的 Edge 窗口使用不同配置文件的问题" />&lt;p>Visual Studio Code 内置的 JavaScript Debugger 调试用的 Edge 配置文件和 Edge 默认的配置文件冲突导致任务栏新建的 Edge 窗口使用的是调试用配置文件。
本文为此提供了一种解决方式。&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="问题">&lt;a href="#%e9%97%ae%e9%a2%98" class="header-anchor">&lt;/a>问题
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>从任务栏新建的 Edge 窗口使用的是其他配置文件。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://thejiahao.github.io/posts/edge-window-different-profile-issue/edge_create_new_window.webp"
width="359"
height="324"
srcset="https://thejiahao.github.io/posts/edge-window-different-profile-issue/edge_create_new_window_hu971af96d7773065ac1d80896ce0cb931_86222_480x0_resize_q100_h2_box_2.webp 480w, https://thejiahao.github.io/posts/edge-window-different-profile-issue/edge_create_new_window_hu971af96d7773065ac1d80896ce0cb931_86222_1024x0_resize_q100_h2_box_2.webp 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="从任务栏中新建 Edge 窗口"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="110"
data-flex-basis="265px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://thejiahao.github.io/posts/edge-window-different-profile-issue/edge_new_window.webp"
width="1052"
height="954"
srcset="https://thejiahao.github.io/posts/edge-window-different-profile-issue/edge_new_window_huef2a939589bca9099b378e0b146fcb69_313266_480x0_resize_q100_h2_box_2.webp 480w, https://thejiahao.github.io/posts/edge-window-different-profile-issue/edge_new_window_huef2a939589bca9099b378e0b146fcb69_313266_1024x0_resize_q100_h2_box_2.webp 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="新窗口使用不同配置文件"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="110"
data-flex-basis="264px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="原因">&lt;a href="#%e5%8e%9f%e5%9b%a0" class="header-anchor">&lt;/a>原因
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>任务栏上的 Edge 启动参数 &lt;code>--profile-directory=Default&lt;/code> 中的配置文件和 VSCode JavaScript Debugger 调试用的 Edge 配置文件 &lt;code>%APPDATA%\Code\User\workspaceStorage\...\ms-vscode.js-debug\.profile\Default&lt;/code> 重名。&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="解决方式">&lt;a href="#%e8%a7%a3%e5%86%b3%e6%96%b9%e5%bc%8f" class="header-anchor">&lt;/a>解决方式
&lt;/h2>&lt;ol>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>将 &lt;code>%LOCALAPPDATA%\Microsoft\Edge\User Data\Default&lt;/code> 中的 Default 配置文件改名，例如 &lt;code>Profile 1&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>将任务栏中快捷方式的启动参数改为新配置文件的名称，例如 &lt;code>--profile-directory=&amp;quot;Profile 1&amp;quot;&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://thejiahao.github.io/posts/edge-window-different-profile-issue/edge_shortcut_properties.webp"
width="381"
height="308"
srcset="https://thejiahao.github.io/posts/edge-window-different-profile-issue/edge_shortcut_properties_hu7f263829790cd6c56f8ff7e168ceada5_92564_480x0_resize_q100_h2_box_2.webp 480w, https://thejiahao.github.io/posts/edge-window-different-profile-issue/edge_shortcut_properties_hu7f263829790cd6c56f8ff7e168ceada5_92564_1024x0_resize_q100_h2_box_2.webp 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="查看任务栏快捷方式的属性"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="123"
data-flex-basis="296px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://thejiahao.github.io/posts/edge-window-different-profile-issue/edge_shortcut_change_properties.webp"
width="421"
height="651"
srcset="https://thejiahao.github.io/posts/edge-window-different-profile-issue/edge_shortcut_change_properties_hu470d8fe5aab7b8341741b51ec7fece85_15084_480x0_resize_q100_h2_box_2.webp 480w, https://thejiahao.github.io/posts/edge-window-different-profile-issue/edge_shortcut_change_properties_hu470d8fe5aab7b8341741b51ec7fece85_15084_1024x0_resize_q100_h2_box_2.webp 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="修改启动参数"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="64"
data-flex-basis="155px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol></description></item><item><title>Windows 下通过 Scoop 为 VS Code 配置 clangd</title><link>https://thejiahao.github.io/posts/windows-vscode-clangd-setup/</link><pubDate>Thu, 12 May 2022 00:00:00 +0200</pubDate><guid>https://thejiahao.github.io/posts/windows-vscode-clangd-setup/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://thejiahao.github.io/posts/windows-vscode-clangd-setup/clangd_logo.svg" alt="Featured image of post Windows 下通过 Scoop 为 VS Code 配置 clangd" />&lt;p>使用 Scoop 安装 &lt;a class="link" href="https://clangd.llvm.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>clangd&lt;/a> 可以自动配置环境变量和避免 Visual Studio Code 找不到 &lt;code>#include&lt;/code>。
本文介绍了通过 Scoop 安装 clangd 的方法。&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="安装方式">&lt;a href="#%e5%ae%89%e8%a3%85%e6%96%b9%e5%bc%8f" class="header-anchor">&lt;/a>安装方式
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>安装 &lt;a class="link" href="https://scoop.sh/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>Scoop&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#abb2bf;background-color:#282c34;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-powershell" data-lang="powershell">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#e5c07b">Invoke-WebRequest&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#e06c75">get&lt;/span>.&lt;span style="color:#e06c75">scoop&lt;/span>.&lt;span style="color:#e06c75">sh&lt;/span> | &lt;span style="color:#e5c07b">Invoke-Expression&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>安装 &lt;a class="link" href="https://winlibs.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>Winlibs&lt;/a> 编译的 MinGW + Clang + clangd&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#abb2bf;background-color:#282c34;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-powershell" data-lang="powershell">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#e06c75">scoop&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#e06c75">install&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#e5c07b">mingw-winlibs&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>VS Code 安装 &lt;a class="link" href="https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=llvm-vs-code-extensions.vscode-clangd" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>clangd&lt;/a> 扩展。&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>